Just published a new blog post diving deep into the world of Jenkins pipelines. 🛠️ If you're into DevOps and automation, this one's for you!

In this post, we will learn the power of declarative Jenkins pipelines and how they play along with environment variables. 💡

✅ Task : Create a job for an application using declarative pipeline where the job automatically clones the code from github repo, builds the image, pushes the code to docker-hub and deploys it.
